--- INVESTIGATION 8: Double-counting of 2-paths ---
  Each 2-path (a,b,c) touches 3 vertices: a (first), b (middle), c (last)
  Sum over v of #(2-paths through v) = 3 * #(2-paths)
  t3=0: sum_through_v = 30, 3*#2paths = 30, match: True
  t3=0: sum_through_v = 30, 3*#2paths = 30, match: True
