--- INVESTIGATION 9: rank_from_v (zeroing approach) vs rank_drop ---
  rank_from_v = rank(bd @ omega) - rank(bd @ omega with v-paths zeroed)
  rank_drop = B1_rank(T) - B1_rank(T\v)
  These measure different things: zeroing vs deletion
  Total vertices: 3600
  Diff=0: 2040
